content: Damaged Fuel Filter Housing May Cause Fuel Leak

Jayco, Inc. (Jayco) is recalling certain 2025 Entegra Aspire, 2025-2026 Entegra Anthem, and Cornerstone motorhomes.  The fuel filter housing may become damaged from contact with the rear cap support bracket, causing a fuel leak.A fuel leak in the presence of an ignition source increases the risk of a fire.

Number of Units Affected: 34.0
